<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Email</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { width: 90%; max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px; }
        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; margin: 20px 0; background-color: #007bff; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; }
        .footer { margin-top: 20px; font-size: 0.9em; color: #777; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Hello {{username}},</h2>
        <p>Thank you for registering with {{appName}}! Please verify your email address to complete your registration and activate your account.</p>
        <p>Click the button below to verify your email:</p>
        <a href="{{verificationLink}}" class="button">Verify Email Address</a>
        <p>If the button above doesn't work, copy and paste the following link into your web browser:</p>
        <p><a href="{{verificationLink}}">{{verificationLink}}</a></p>
        <p>If you did not create an account with {{appName}}, please disregard this email.</p>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thanks,<br/>The {{appName}} Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
